{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":205,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-10T20:55:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223783406\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589143504\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160817\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Lo Var Lachland\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Lo Var Lachland said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPopping in from my absence and quarantine to ask if there is any ETA on the \u0022array\u0022 bug being fixed on main profiles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSoon\u003Csup\u003ETM\u003C/sup\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAccording to my limited knowledge, the bug is on IPS\u0027 end, not ours, so it came packaged with the forum software. You might have to ask Invision Power directly. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-10T20:55:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe scrolling only happens when you\u0027re:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Using a browser which supports it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Your screen size doesn\u0027t allow the default width of the signature area.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn my screen and with Microsoft Edge, there isn\u0027t any scrolling in my signature area.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-10T20:59:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223783413\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221589144110\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe scrolling only happens when you\u0027re:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Using a browser which supports it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Your screen size doesn\u0027t allow the default width of the signature area.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOn my screen and with Microsoft Edge, there isn\u0027t any scrolling in my signature area.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay maybe I am a tech boomer. I dunno. Thanks anyway. Quarantine has screwed my head over to be sure.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-10T21:01:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topi