ows exactly how this software handles that... I was told the time between the posts before merger wasn\u0027t automatic was at least a minute or two.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Etis a mystery that shall never be solved.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Ebut thanks for helping \u003Cimg alt=\u0022^_^\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022^_^\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"XB-70A","CreatedById":144985,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-05-26T01:25:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/185809-hansonkerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022185809\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/185809-hansonkerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HansonKerman\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Many of us already saw it in the Number Wars 2 topic (in my case I stopped counting how many times). It appears most often when many users are posting simultaneously or\u00A0without leaving enough time between each replies.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/64714-gargamel/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002264714\u0022 href=\u0022https://for